---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const prompt = `I have uploaded a sample dealer sales report for an Australian automotive company.

Please analyse it and provide:
1. The key trends by model and state
2. Any dealers that appear to be underperforming
3. Any unusual movements or outliers
4. Three recommended actions for management
5. A short executive summary suitable for a General Manager

Present the findings in a table first, then a concise summary.`;
---
<Layout title="Analyse Excel | AI Hub">
  <section class="recipe">
    <div class="eyebrow">📊 Try it · 5 min</div>
    <h1>Analyse Excel without staring at Excel.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Use this when you have sales reports, warranty costs, inventory exports, finance summaries or campaign results and need trends fast.</p>
    <div class="panel"><h2>What to do</h2><ol><li>Download the sample file.</li><li>Upload it to ChatGPT or Claude.</li><li>Copy the prompt below.</li><li>Ask follow-up questions until the answer is useful.</li></ol><a class="btn primary" href={`${base}downloads/dealer-sales-sample.csv`} download>Download sample CSV</a></div>
    <div class="panel"><h2>Prompt</h2><div class="prompt">{prompt}</div><button class="btn copy" data-copy={prompt}>Copy prompt</button></div>
    <div class="kevin"><div class="kevin-avatar">K</div><p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)"><b>Kevin warning:</b> AI can describe trends, but you still need to check the raw numbers before making decisions.</p></div>
  </section>
</Layout>
